 <div id="cdm-zone-00">
   &nbsp; 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Abyss Greatsword</strong> is a <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Weapons" href="/Weapons" target="">Weapon</a> in <strong>Dark Souls</strong> and <strong>Dark Souls Remastered</strong>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Artorias of the Abyss (Expansion)" href="/Artorias+of+the+Abyss+(Expansion)">(AotA only)</a></p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<blockquote> 
 <p>This greatsword belonged to Lord Gwyn's Knight Artorias, who fell to the Abyss.<br> Swallowed by the Dark with its master, this sword is tainted by the Abyss, and now its strength reflects its wielder's humanity."</p> 
 <p>&nbsp;</p> 
</blockquote> 
<h3 class="bonfire">How to Get&nbsp;/ Where to Find the Abyss Greatsword</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Ascension with the <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Soul of Artorias" href="/Soul+of+Artorias">Soul of Artorias</a> and any normal +10 <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Greatswords" href="/Greatswords">Greatsword</a>, <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Straight Swords" href="/Straight+Swords">Straight Sword</a> or <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Daggers" href="/Daggers">Dagger</a> (except <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Broken Straight Sword" href="/Broken+Straight+Sword">Broken Straight Sword</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link wiki_tooltip" title="Dark Souls Straight Sword Hilt" href="/Straight+Sword+Hilt">Straight Sword Hilt</a>).</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Notes:<strong><br></strong></h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Can be given to <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Kingseeker Frampt" href="/Kingseeker+Frampt">Kingseeker Frampt</a>&nbsp;to receive&nbsp;50 Souls.</li> 
 <li><strong>Abyss Greatsword</strong> can be upgraded by using <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Demon Titanite" href="/Demon+Titanite">Demon Titanite</a>.</li> 
 <li>Unlike the <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Greatsword of Artorias" href="/Greatsword+of+Artorias">Greatsword of Artorias</a> (or the <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Greatsword of Artorias (Cursed)" href="/Greatsword+of+Artorias+(Cursed)">Cursed</a> version), Abyss Greatsword does not scale with Intelligence or Faith.&nbsp;</li> 
 <li>The sword's damage scales with <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Humanity" href="/Humanity">Humanity</a> and caps at 10. <span style="line-height: 1.5;">The difference in attack rating between 0 and 10 Humanity is around 74 at minimum stat requirements.</span></li> 
 <li>One-handed R2 is a 360-degree spin that hits twice. Two-handed R2 is a somersault that brings the blade swinging down overhead causing a powerful knockdown.</li> 
 <li>This sword requires only Strength and Dexterity for the Physical damage scaling. It is still usable even without meeting the Intelligence and Faith requirement, except it bounces back for every hit.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>&nbsp;<img src="/file/Dark-Souls/abyss-greatsword-onhand-large.jpg" alt="abyss greatsword onhand large" width="227" height="298"></p> 
<div class="clearfix">
  &nbsp; 
</div> 
<h3 class="bonfire"><a name="Abyss Greatsword"></a>Abyss Greatsword Upgrade Table</h3> 
<p><a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Unique Upgrades" href="/Unique+Upgrades">Demon Titanite</a> weapon upgrades&nbsp; can only be applied to <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Boss Soul Weapons" href="/Boss+Soul+Weapons" target="">Boss Soul Weapons</a>&nbsp;forged at the&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Giant Blacksmith" href="/Giant+Blacksmith" target="">Giant Blacksmith</a>&nbsp;in <a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Anor Londo" href="/Anor+Londo">Anor Londo</a>.<br>Regular Reinforcement Scales 55% for&nbsp;<img title="strength_dark_souls.jpg" src="/file/Dark-Souls/strength_dark_souls.jpg" alt="strength dark souls"><a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Strength" href="/Strength" target="">Strength</a>&nbsp;and 55% for&nbsp;<img title="dexterity_dark_souls.jpg" src="/file/Dark-Souls/dexterity_dark_souls.jpg" alt="dexterity dark souls"><a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Dexterity" href="/Dexterity" target="">Dexterity</a>&nbsp;to increase your AR. Also, gives 100 critical bonus.<br>To reach max, you need: 25,000 Souls and 10&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Demon Titanite" href="/Demon+Titanite"><img title="demon_titanite_dark_souls_s" src="/file/Dark-Souls/demon_titanite_dark_souls_s.png" alt="demon titanite dark souls s" width="16" height="18"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Dark Souls Demon Titanite" href="/Demon+Titanite" target="">Demon Titanite</a>.</p> 
